<P>THE RAMBLER.</P>
<P>VOLUME THE SIXTH.</P>
<Q><L>Nullius addictus jurare in verba magi&s;tri,</L>
<L>Quo me cunque rapit tempe&s;tas, deferor ho&s;pes.</L>
<BIBL>HOR.</BIBL></Q>
