<DIV1 N="volume 3" TYPE="table of contents">
<PB REF="306">
<HEAD>CONTENTS OF THE THIRD VOLUME.</HEAD>
<LIST>
<ITEM>NUMB. 71 No man believes that his own life will be &s;hort. Page 1</ITEM>
<ITEM>NUMB. 72 The nece&s;&s;ity of good-humour. Page 8</ITEM>
