</LG>
<BIBL>DRYDEN.</BIBL></Q></ITEM>
<ITEM>NUMB. 81
<Q><LG>
<L>Hear, and be ju&s;t.</L>
</LG></Q></ITEM>
<ITEM>NUMB. 82
<Q><LG>
<L>Who buys without di&s;cretion, buys to &s;ell.</L>
</LG></Q></ITEM>
<ITEM>NUMB. 83
<Q><LG>
<L>All u&s;ele&s;s &s;cience is an empty boa&s;t.</L>
</LG></Q>
<Q><LG>
<L>&mdash;Who&s;o ta&s;tes,</L>
<L>Infatiate riots in the &s;weet repa&s;ts;</L>
