<L>You pry, and frown, and growl, and chide,</L>
<L>And &s;carce will lay the rod a&s;ide.</L>
</LG>
<BIBL>F. LEWIS.</BIBL></Q></ITEM>
<ITEM>NUMB. 85
<Q><LG>
